text: Hernando Delgado (born 5 November 1937) is a Spanish wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman lightweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Spain Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Madrid
